@page
@model FAQModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "FAQ";
}

<section class="py-5 my-5">
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row mb-2">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-xl-6 text-center mx-auto">
                <h2 class="display-6 fw-bold mb-5"><span class="pb-3" style="text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-color: #F27052;">FAQ<br></span></h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-5">Find the answers for the most frequently asked questions below.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mb-2">
            <div class="col-md-8 mx-auto">
                <div class="accordion text-muted" role="tablist" id="accordion-1">
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" role="tab"><button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#accordion-1 .item-1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="accordion-1 .item-1">Can I get a refund if I can’t go for a holiday in a planned time?</button></h2>
                        <div class="accordion-collapse collapse show item-1" role="tabpanel" data-bs-parent="#accordion-1">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>Yes, We are doing refunds or we can offer you the trip in different time, but you need to cancel your reservation before 24hrs before trip.  Contact with us.</p>
                                <p class="mb-0">  Contact with us via contact page on the top ⬆️ </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" role="tab"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#accordion-1 .item-2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1 .item-2">Do I need to give my middle names for the order?</button></h2>
                        <div class="accordion-collapse collapse item-2" role="tabpanel" data-bs-parent="#accordion-1">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p class="mb-0">
                                    No, You don’t need. Just name and surname with your personal details, the same as on your travel document.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" role="tab"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#accordion-1 .item-3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1 .item-3">Does the cancellation of my trip cost me a fee? </button></h2>
                        <div class="accordion-collapse collapse item-3" role="tabpanel" data-bs-parent="#accordion-1">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p class="mb-0">No, it’s free! Just enjoy our holidays offers in the different time.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" role="tab"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#accordion-1 .item-4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1 .item-4">How can I contact with MTM Holiday ? </button></h2>
                        <div class="accordion-collapse collapse item-4" role="tabpanel" data-bs-parent="#accordion-1">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p class="mb-0">
                                    Just click below link here:
                                    <div class="my-2"><a class="btn btn-light fs-5 py-2 px-4" role="button" href="Contacts">Contact us!</a></div>
                                    Our assistant will answer you as soon as possible.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                     <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" role="tab"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#accordion-1 .item-5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1 .item-5">Where can I find order confirmation ?  </button></h2>
                        <div class="accordion-collapse collapse item-5" role="tabpanel" data-bs-parent="#accordion-1">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p class="mb-0">Order confirmation you can find on your account and also we are sending order confirmation to a given email address.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" role="tab"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#accordion-1 .item-6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1 .item-6"> How can I pay for my order? </button></h2>
                        <div class="accordion-collapse collapse item-6" role="tabpanel" data-bs-parent="#accordion-1">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p class="mb-0">We are accepting all debit or credit cards.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" role="tab"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#accordion-1 .item-7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1 .item-7">  Are you accepting gift cards? </button></h2>
                        <div class="accordion-collapse collapse item-7" role="tabpanel" data-bs-parent="#accordion-1">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p class="mb-0">
                                    Sorry, unfortunately we are not accepting any gift cards.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" role="tab"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#accordion-1 .item-8" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1 .item-8"> What can I do if my card it’s not working on this website? </button></h2>
                        <div class="accordion-collapse collapse item-8" role="tabpanel" data-bs-parent="#accordion-1">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p class="mb-0">Just contact with us via contact form or if it’s a problem with your card - try to call the bank or check your limits on your online bank account.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" role="tab"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#accordion-1 .item-9" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1 .item-9"> What is the best date to go on holidays ? </button></h2>
                        <div class="accordion-collapse collapse item-9" role="tabpanel" data-bs-parent="#accordion-1">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p class="mb-0">
                                    It’s hard to say, that’s depends what you want to do during your holidays, but in case of beach holidays we are thinking that the best in case of the weather is time between May-September.

                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

